Game information:

Favorite heroes of the set of boys and girls - Buzz, Woody and Jessie -
a new computer game based on the eponymous animated film Disney / Pixar!
Just two game modes to choose from: you can relive the events cartoon
and save all your favorite toys Andy or create your own adventures in
the "box of toys." At your disposal will be a town in the Wild West,
which you can arrange as you wish. Perform a job, build new homes,
change clothes and hairstyles, go captivating mini-games.
With complete freedom of action play was incredibly interesting!
Plug imagination!

Game Features:

Favorite characters in the new game - adventure continues!
Scene Mode - Plunge into heroic adventures based on the cartoon.
"A box of toys" - create and rejoice in their own unique town.
